Package com.irurueta.navigation.indoor.position

Estimates positions using WiFi/Beacons signals.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PositionEstimatorListener<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
    Listener to be notified of events such as when estimation starts or ends.
    RobustPositionEstimatorListener<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
    Listener to be notified of events produced by a robust position estimator when estimation starts, ends or when progress changes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LinearPositionEstimator<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
    Linearly estimates position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
    LinearPositionEstimator2D
    Linearly estimates 2D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
    LinearPositionEstimator3D
    Linearly estimates 3D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
    LMedSRobustPositionEstimator2D
    Robustly estimates 2D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using RANSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    LMedSRobustPositionEstimator3D
    Robustly estimates 3D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using RANSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    MSACRobustPositionEstimator2D
    Robustly estimates 2D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using MSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    MSACRobustPositionEstimator3D
    Robustly estimates 3D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using MSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    NonLinearPositionEstimator<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
    Estimates position non-linearly using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
    NonLinearPositionEstimator2D
    Estimates 2D position non-linearly using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
    NonLinearPositionEstimator3D
    Estimates 3D position non-linearly using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
    PositionEstimator<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
    Base class for position estimators using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
    PositionEstimatorHelper
    Utility class that converts located radio sources and fingerprints into positions, distances and distance standard deviations that can be used to solve the trilateration problem.
    PROMedSRobustPositionEstimator2D
    Robustly estimates 2D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using PROMedS algorithm to discard outliers.
    PROMedSRobustPositionEstimator3D
    Robustly estimates 3D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using PROMedS algorithm to discard outliers.
    PROSACRobustPositionEstimator2D
    Robustly estimates 2D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using PROSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    PROSACRobustPositionEstimator3D
    Robustly estimates 3D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using PROSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    RANSACRobustPositionEstimator2D
    Robustly estimates 2D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using RANSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    RANSACRobustPositionEstimator3D
    Robustly estimates 2D position using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations and using RANSAC algorithm to discard outliers.
    RobustPositionEstimator<P extends com.irurueta.geometry.Point>
    Base class for robust position estimators using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
    RobustPositionEstimator2D
    Base class for 2D robust position estimators using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
    RobustPositionEstimator3D
    Base class for 3D robust position estimators using located radio sources and their readings at unknown locations.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    PositionEstimationException
    Exception raised if position estimation fails.
